            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <supplied reason="lost">Recte igitur homines ab illo tempore recenseant vitae</supplied> <lb n="2"/><supplied reason="lost">ini</supplied>tiu&amp;lt;m=IA&amp;gt; &amp;lt;q=O&amp;gt;uod paenitendi &amp;lt;f=E&amp;gt;uerit natos se esse &amp;lt;fi=EL&amp;gt;nis <lb n="3"/>cum&amp;lt;q=O&amp;gt;ue non ullo ex die feliciora et &amp;lt;p=O&amp;gt;r&amp;lt;iv=N&amp;gt;at&amp;lt;i=V&amp;gt;m (singulis) et uni<lb break="no" n="4"/>versis publice trahi possint aus&amp;lt;pici=SELIP&amp;gt;a &amp;lt;q=O&amp;gt;uam ex eo &amp;lt;q=O&amp;gt;uem felicissi<lb break="no" n="5"/>mum communiter (noverunt) fere autem omnium in Asia &amp;lt;ci=EL&amp;gt;vitatium idem <lb n="6"/>tempus &amp;lt;a=M&amp;gt;nni novi initium macis&amp;lt;t=E&amp;gt;ratuum <note>sic</note> sit in &amp;lt;q=O&amp;gt;uod &amp;lt;divin=PONEV&amp;gt;i<lb break="no" n="7"/>t&amp;lt;us=O&amp;gt; videlicet ut honoraretur &amp;lt;p=O&amp;gt;rin&amp;lt;ci=O&amp;gt;pis nostri natalis incidit vel <lb n="8"/>&amp;lt;q=O&amp;gt;uia tot erca <note>sic</note> divina merita cratin <note>sic</note> esse di&amp;lt;ff=P&amp;gt;icile est nisi omnis <lb n="9"/>pietatis tem<expan><ex>p</ex><abbr>tetu</abbr></expan>&amp;lt;r=A&amp;gt; materia vel &amp;lt;q=SO&amp;gt;uia iu<expan><ex>b</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan><surplus>u</surplus>n&amp;lt;d=O&amp;gt;us propria <expan><ex>q</ex><abbr>uis</abbr></expan>&amp;lt;q=O&amp;gt;ue <lb n="10"/>laetitia ingre&amp;lt;d=SSV&amp;gt;i <expan><abbr>honore</abbr><ex>m</ex></expan> in<surplus>i</surplus>traturus publicum videtur <supplied reason="lost">d</supplied>iem <lb n="11"/><supplied reason="lost">quem Graeci suo nomine diem nean numenian appellant eum</supplied> <lb n="12"/><supplied reason="lost">clarissimi viri Caesaris diem natalem haberi</supplied> 
